title: Chrishena Stanley of The Stanley Team Selected for "Selling It: In The ATL"
text:
Chrishena Stanley of The Stanley Team Selected for "Selling It: In The ATL"
Chrishena Stanley of The Stanley Team Atlanta will be starring in the new series "Selling It: In The ATL" to air on WE tv this November.
Atlanta, GA, October 20, 2015 --( PR.com )-- Chrishena Stanley of The Stanley Team Atlanta will be staring in the new WE tv series "Selling It: In The ATL." The six-episode hour-long series, which comes on the heels of the freshman season of Cutting It: In The ATL, will premiere at 10 PM Thursday, November 5.
Chrishena will be staring along with six other diverse female professionals who are changing the definition of real estate in Atlanta. “I can’t stress enough how excited I am to be included in Selling It. It has been a great experience in every way, and allows me to showcase the wonderful attributes of a thriving and evolving Atlanta,” said Chrishena Stanley. “While there are certainly challenges to be faced every day, I find real estate to highly rewarding. In what other business can you truly help make a house a home?
About Chrishena Stanley :
Chrishena Stanley is an Associate Broker with Coldwell Banker Residential Brokerage in Atlanta GA., and a principal of The Stanley Team of Atlanta.
